                    "body": "In conjunction with https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ARROW-2367 now I'm totally confused. \r\n\r\nAre the array lengths `arrow format` specific or implementation specific? \r\nWhat are the actual limits of an array? Why are these limits datatype dependent?\r\n\r\nThe [list offset bulletpoint|https://github.com/apache/arrow/blob/master/format/Layout.md#list-type] in the format is also misleading.",
