                    "body": "{quote}Are the array lengths `arrow format` specific or implementation specific?{quote}\r\n\r\nI don't know. But array length is not part of array data, only metadata, so I guess implementations are free to represent it as they prefer?\r\n\r\n{quote}The [list offset bulletpoint|https://github.com/apache/arrow/blob/master/format/Layout.md#list-type] in the format is also misleading.{quote}\r\n\r\nCan you explain what looks misleading to you?\u00a0",
